                  <summary>The names of Mary in various languages (f. i r); Anaphora of Our Lady Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, Qǝddase Maryam Gwäs’a, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡ (f<locus target="#1r"/>-36v); Image of Mary of Edom. መልክአ፡ ኤዶም. Chaîne, Répertoire 221 (f<locus target="#37r"/>-39v); Asmat prayer (<locus target="#40v"/>)</summary>
